2. Show a clear notification: "Loading AI model into memory... this takes about a minute on first use"
3. Show progress or at least an animated indicator so the user knows it is working
4. After first load, set keep_alive=-1 so the model stays in memory

The weekly optimization agent should also factor in cold-load time when ranking local providers.
